	<p style="font-size:25px;text-align:center"><strong> Remember: </strong></p>

	<div class="well">
		<p style="font-size:15px">
		Learning how to safely backpack takes time: start with single-day hikes and build up to multi-day and week backpacking trips. Make sure you are as prepared as possible by testing your gear in the field, speaking to experienced hikers and backpacking professionals, and following our guidelines! 
		</p>
